(3517, 109130, 'Asian Reggae Allstars Vol. 1', 'O-Brothaz Productions presents the first compilation of reggae artists from Asian countries and those artists living in Asian countries who are pushing the growing reggae movement.  This first of the compilation series is a stepping stone to the world of reggae that has been developing through the Asian countries.  For the first time the various styles of reggae; roots, lovers rock, new roots, and dancehall are all presented by various artists from an array of Asian countries including Indonesia, Taiwan, Japan, Philippines, Malaysia, Sri Lanka and more.', '2011-06-29 00:00:00', 0, 1, 11, 'Oliver "Lion" Harley', 'O-Brothaz Productions', 0, '', 1, 0, '2011-06-30 10:56:10', '2015-02-16 15:47:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3518, 11164, '城市．愛', '常看到朋友說著，台南的美食與人文、花蓮的美景與悠閒。身在台北的朋友抱怨著空氣、抱怨著擁擠、抱怨一切。不得已而來到台北的人心中總懷抱著故鄉，然而生長在台北的人卻無處可去。這裡雖然被嫌棄，卻仍然是我們城市人的故鄉，而故鄉就是那種，無論如何不能捨棄的事物吧。簡直難以想像捨棄了源頭，人還會剩下什麼。因此總想為它做些什麼，為它改變什麼。如果可以的話，多為它辯護一點，多為它堅持或爭取一點。\r\n\r\nCover Design: 陳青琳', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 0, 2, 2, 'Trying Times', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2011-06-30 20:14:54', '2015-02-16 15:47:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
